snippet.textDisplay:
Gurdas Maan is in a class and league of his own. Can't believe it's taken MTV Coke Studios so long to get him to feature on this but finally they made it happen. Respect to Diljit for trying his best alongside Gurdas Maan but the legend outshines not only Diljit but every other element on the screen and on the soundtrack. 
GM's charisma, energy and passion is on another level. This collaboration highlights his superiority in the Punjabi music scene in such a simple manner. Big love!
snippet.textOriginal:
Gurdas Maan is in a class and league of his own. Can't believe it's taken MTV Coke Studios so long to get him to feature on this but finally they made it happen. Respect to Diljit for trying his best alongside Gurdas Maan but the legend outshines not only Diljit but every other element on the screen and on the soundtrack.
